track_notes: Nice long hike on the AT. Did it in one day. I would probably do an over night along the way next time.

This is the way to the summit via a short access road from inside the development that ties in with the AT.  The result is a much shorter hike than the one from Sams Gap.   Access to this road is by permission only.
track_title: W4T/SU-010 Big Bald Summit Access Inside Development

track_notes: STARTS AT A FOREST SERVICE ROAD. CUTS OFF A LITTLE OVER 2 MILES FROM THE LONGER HIKE. NO PERMISSION REQUIRED.
Gps track from Flag Pond exit since my phone would not recognize the forest road. The road is fair. You can also come from the NC side but road is worse.
